      "t_start": 104.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 18.0,
      "narration_text": "E\u2081 and E\u2082 for a 1 nm box: 0.376 eV and 1.505 eV. Difference: 1.129 eV. Frequency: 2.73 \u00d7 10\u00b9\u2074 Hz \u2014 deep ultraviolet. The probability cloud sloshes back and forth 273 trillion times per second.",
