      "t_start": 122.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "A stationary state is not static. Its phase rotates invisibly. Superpose two and the rotation becomes real \u2014 a beating, oscillating probability cloud. That beat is every spectral line ever measured. That is quantum mechanics.",
